    {
      "para_id": "Q001920.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Enlil , king of all land , his master , Išbi-Erra , the powerful king , the king of his land , fashioned a lofty balaĝ - drum , which ... the heart , and dedicated it to him for his well-being ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001920.12",
      "line_range": "12",
      "translation": "(12) The name of this balaĝ - drum is “Išbi-Erra puts ( his ) trust in Enlil.”"
    }
  ],
